            "text": "Understanding Kokoro Python Architecture"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Kokoro python leverages a transformer-based design optimized for low-latency responses. Key components include the inference engine, which supports batched processing, and a modular API layer that integrates with frameworks like FastAPI or Flask. Ensure your environment has Python 3.8+ and sufficient GPU resources for optimal performance."
          }
