            "type": "text",
            "text": "pip install kokoro-python",
            "code": true
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ". Configure the model using a YAML file to specify parameters such as model path, device allocation (CPU/GPU), and logging levels. For containerized deployments, use Docker images with pre-installed dependencies to maintain consistency across environments."
          }
